    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 25 },
      "id": 12,
      "options": {
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "## Setup checklist to activate all panels\n\n| Panel | Requires | How |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Kafka** status | `kafka-exporter` container | Add `danielqsj/kafka-exporter` to `docker-compose.yml`, target `kafka:29092` |\n| **Consumer Lag** | `kafka-exporter` | Same as above — metric `kafka_consumergroup_lag` |\n| **Topic Rate** | `kafka-exporter` | Same as above — metric `kafka_topic_partition_current_offset` |\n| **Zookeeper** status | JMX Exporter java agent | Attach agent to `cp-zookeeper`, expose port 7072 |\n| **Kafka JMX** | JMX Exporter java agent | Attach agent to `cp-kafka`, expose port 7071 |\n| **MinIO** status | Bearer token | Run `mc admin prometheus generate local` and add `bearer_token` to `prometheus.yml` |\n| **CPU / Memory** | cAdvisor | Add `gcr.io/cadvisor/cadvisor` to `docker-compose.yml`, target port 8080 |\n\nPrometheus config is at `prometheus/prometheus.yml` — each job has a ready-to-use `docker-compose` snippet in the comments.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Setup Notes",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    }

